{"type":"article","id":8802,"title":"[搬运+整合] 香港暴徙的谎言","uid":9677,"topics":[2143,17,2158],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7IIUeVc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7IIUeVc.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7IIUeVc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n李家超说辞：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pryj8GH6Y4g\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pryj8GH6Y4g</a><br>\n<br>\nRTHK整合721资讯（多番发现警车目睹事件发生）：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;t=665s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=16CiwPChpr0&amp;t=665s</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dmblupG.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dmblupG.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dmblupG.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关影片：<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gxVMe35if4o\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gxVMe35if4o</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mqk858k.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mqk858k.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mqk858k.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关报导「今晚开香槟庆祝啊！」：<br>\n<br>\n[url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Ch_v5Jn9WA][/url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0tzHSEP0rk\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0tzHSEP0rk</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LbV9sRF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LbV9sRF.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LbV9sRF.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n记者会的说辞：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5dce64c4e6038368289871a8/%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%91%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6-%E7%89%87%E4%B8%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%A5%E6%B2%99\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5dce64c4e6038368289871a8/%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%91%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6-%E7%89%87%E4%B8%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%8A%A9%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%8A%E5%82%B7%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%8A%E6%B3%A5%E6%B2%99</a><br>\n<br>\n实际的影片：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4NAIojmfRl4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4NAIojmfRl4</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ymfyyhe.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ymfyyhe.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ymfyyhe.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n4吋月饼餐刀描述为9吋刀：<br>\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190916/bkn-20190916114524545-0916_00822_001.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190916/bkn-20190916114524545-0916_00822_001.html</a><br>\n<br>\n拔枪，事源警察拘捕一名路人：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/592819781246534/?v=592819781246534\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/onccnews/videos/592819781246534/?v=592819781246534</a><br>\n<br>\n记者会解释激光枪：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hIi3ZaG8vGo\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hIi3ZaG8vGo</a><br>\n<br>\n医生解释激光枪：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v2uo4THg1gI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v2uo4THg1gI</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kNs5kQM.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kNs5kQM.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kNs5kQM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关片段：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1iN4XKHKgT4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1iN4XKHKgT4</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OApE9ke.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OApE9ke.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OApE9ke.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n汽车上的闭录电视片段：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XH7XkxoOSBs\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XH7XkxoOSBs</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xBKw6ZK.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xBKw6ZK.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xBKw6ZK.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n中大教授亲述当日经过：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/posts/2519299994773988\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/posts/2519299994773988</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/photos/a.701343143236358/2519545634749424\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaichil/photos/a.701343143236358/2519545634749424</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HaYHp17.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HaYHp17.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/HaYHp17.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n记者二噁英中毒相关报导：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492229-20191114.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492229-20191114.htm</a><br>\n<br>\n警方记者会回应：「我唔係化学专家，我唔知，但唔好入我数」<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmPmvTjFCSc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmPmvTjFCSc</a><br>\n<br>\n英国牛津大学流行病学者陈嘉鸿博士反驳这说法：「催泪烟的主要物质CS须在高温燃烧下才有机会衍生大量毒素，释放类二恶英及其他有毒物质，但若要透过焚烧塑料释出二恶英，燃烧的需要是含氯有机物，例如PVC胶，再加上一些金属粒子，在摄氏200度至450度之间燃烧才可以，故此，燃烧路障虽然有可能释放二恶英，但「不是那么容易」。」<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191116-%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BC%E8%BF%91%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9F%93%E4%BA%8C%E6%83%A1%E8%8B%B1%E9%A1%9E%E7%97%85-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E8%88%87%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191116-%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E7%99%BC%E8%BF%91%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88-%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9F%93%E4%BA%8C%E6%83%A1%E8%8B%B1%E9%A1%9E%E7%97%85-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E8%88%87%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/l8gJDCE.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/l8gJDCE.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/l8gJDCE.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n警方于记者会回应虐打老人事件，称不知医护病房有CCTV。而事实上CCTV的告示就贴在病房门口，証明警方接获投诉但不积极处理。<br>\n<br>\n相关报导：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/366037/%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E9%86%89%E7%BF%81%E9%81%AD-%E7%A7%81%E5%88%91-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1-%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E9%96%80%E7%89%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%96%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/366037/%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%A5%E9%86%89%E7%BF%81%E9%81%AD-%E7%A7%81%E5%88%91-%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%84%E5%BD%B1-%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E9%96%80%E7%89%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%96%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/MOBbZVF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MOBbZVF.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/MOBbZVF.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/oExHNtm.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oExHNtm.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/oExHNtm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n警方记者会称：「乔装同事不会做违法的事」<br>\n<br>\n香港市民拍摄到扔燃烧弹的人士头部背后有红色闪灯<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ca3-1VJ_ftg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ca3-1VJ_ftg</a><br>\n<br>\n警方当晚派出的乔装人士身上都有蓝色或红色识别灯（部份后来被揭穿并拿出步枪）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtnXOguM278\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtnXOguM278</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/W4CLc8w.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W4CLc8w.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W4CLc8w.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n有没有使用过期催泪弹？<br>\n<br>\n前：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3LcZm4ttcA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F3LcZm4ttcA</a><br>\n<br>\n后（1:39）：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fByIVRfJnDQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fByIVRfJnDQ</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mf7JPu8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mf7JPu8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mf7JPu8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n警方表示：「很多人向警方表达，不敢表达自己的意见，这不是我熟识的香港。」<br>\n<br>\n少年表示：「你们的良心在哪裡？」，后被警方追捕。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wV-Oj-xXdQM\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wV-Oj-xXdQM</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kewq8el.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kewq8el.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kewq8el.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n警务处处长认为，有一半警察被指控过犯罪。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jzwn0pZ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jzwn0pZ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jzwn0pZ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关影片：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D0roLFAZng0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D0roLFAZng0</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QWZhiBC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QWZhiBC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QWZhiBC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n香港警察的「互相尊重」论<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ZUFyWQ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ZUFyWQ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ZUFyWQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关报导：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/383653/10-7%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C-19%E6%AD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%AD%95%E5%A9%A6%E9%80%81%E5%B1%AF%E9%86%AB-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%88%E7%94%A2%E5%89%8D%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E6%83%B9%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%8B%B8%E9%9B%A2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/383653/10-7%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C-19%E6%AD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E5%AD%95%E5%A9%A6%E9%80%81%E5%B1%AF%E9%86%AB-%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%88%E7%94%A2%E5%89%8D%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E6%83%B9%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%8B%B8%E9%9B%A2</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/VcFtAPy.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VcFtAPy.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/VcFtAPy.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n前：「警方能透过专业判断分识现场中谁是犯人，谁是普通市民。」<br>\n<br>\n后：「警方不能在混乱场合中清楚分辨谁是犯人，谁是普通市民」<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/lIPNM4W.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lIPNM4W.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lIPNM4W.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n前：「示威者投掷垃圾桶，完全冈顾他人性命安全。」<br>\n<br>\n后：防暴警投掷垃圾桶（0:11）：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ayanchiu/status/1180421721867735041\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ayanchiu/status/1180421721867735041</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SgMSDsv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SgMSDsv.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SgMSDsv.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n经长时间训练仍然会射头的。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EvpZb5e.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EvpZb5e.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EvpZb5e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n再次前后不一。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/moTfD1O.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/moTfD1O.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/moTfD1O.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n相关报导：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491968-20191113.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491968-20191113.htm</a><br>\n<br>\n-------------------------------新增內容----------------------------------------------<br>\n<br>\n暴徒曾回應指沒有徵用港鐵，後用英文回應卻指曾徵用港鐵運送被捕人士。<br>\n<br>\n相關報導：<br>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9uZXdzLm5vdy5jb20vaG9tZS9sb2NhbC9wbGF5ZXI_bmV3c0lkPTM3MDM5Mw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370393</a>","date":"2019-11-20","agreeCount":28,"discussionCount":0}